column2: "Okay, okay. We're going to thank them this time!"
"Plan? There is no plan. Let's just play it by ear."
"I'm not very smart, so I doubt thinking would accomplish much anyway."
"At any rate, let's just wing it and do the thinking later!"
"Hahaha... I know that isn't very cast-like, but that's just how I am."
"Alright! Let's go! Where should we start today?"
